item.title: CVE-2022-4117|2024-08-03T01:27:54.505Z -- unknown -- iws
item.description: The IWS WordPress plugin through 1.0 does not properly escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement via an AJAX action available to unauthenticated users, leading to an unauthenticated SQL injection.
